                                left flyleaf b side (f. ixb)</locus>: <q xml:lang="en">Bibliotheca
                                Lindesiana</q> with pencilled shelfmark <q xml:lang="en">F/4</q>.<lb/>
                            <locus from="Inner_back_cover" to="Inner_back_cover">Left
